{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, Martin, in his last visit when he came home-- by that time, he was a reporter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And he had all his equipment, and he was going to interview me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And he said mummy, I would like to tell you the story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "I mean, this was 10 years ago-- 12 years ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And we started, and I broke down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "So he said, well, never mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "We'll do it another time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "Well, there wasn't another time, because he was killed soon after that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all the time, I felt that I had-- I wanted to talk about it not only as a historical document, but also to tell the family, in a way, in a continuous way.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I hope-- but then, you see, I think that I haven't done it well, either.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's difficult to find-- it's difficult to express in words [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the nightmarish years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't just one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this-- this terrible fear, which was in us, this helplessness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- the cruelty, the humiliation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's unbearable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's very difficult to describe it in words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of the writing is very good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I hope that-- that people will learn something from that period.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was, again, doubly broken down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I started walking back, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've-- I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first Jewish community-- Jewish people I met was in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know Czestochowa is near Auschwitz, next to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was already a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went over there, because I was in a terrible state.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- so they gave me some money to support.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were two young men who interviewed the people as they were coming back.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
